Package com.amplifyframework.datastore.storage.sqlite.adapter

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SQLiteColumn
    Adapts a ModelField with additional information to assist in representing and processing a SQLite column.
    SQLiteColumn.Builder
    The builder instance to construct immutable instance of SQLite column.
    SQLiteTable
    Adapts a ModelSchema with additional information to assist in representing and processing a SQLite table.
    SQLiteTable.Builder
    A builder to construct immutable SQLite table.
    SQLPredicate
    SQL Predicate adapter that adapts QueryPredicate to be compatible with SQLite use-cases.
